description	"Sith Miraluka

^2Weaponry:
- Dual Lightsabers
-- Dual Style Only
-- Saber Defense   (3)
-- Blaster Defense (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Pull (3)
- Sight (Sense 3, Stat viewer)

^8Attributes:
- Mind Trick Resistance
- Force Shrouding (Invisible to Force Sense)
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (1)

^3Abilities:
- Force Healing (Health dispenser)

Blinded only physically, the Miraluka have trained themselves to see through the force and effectively through
solid objects.
The Miraluka were naturally attuned to the Force and find that such powers as healing and stealth come naturally to them.
"